    >
      Brewed to perfection
    </h2>
    <p>
      <b class="text-lg">Opening hours:</b>
      <br /><br />
      Mon - Thu: 11:00 AM - 9:00 PM <br /><br />
      Fri - Sat: 11:00 AM - 10:00 PM <br /><br />
      Sun: 12:00 PM - 8:00 PM
    </p>
    <p class="my-10">
      <b class="text-lg">Phone:</b>
      <br /><br />
      (555) 987-6543
    </p>
    <p class="mb-10">
      <b class="text-lg">Location:</b>
      <br /><br />
      Burger Haven <br />
      123 Burger Lane <br />
      Food City, FC 12345
    </p>
